{"tid":944823,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"VTC無端端改我班","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T12:15:52.000Z","uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"086c2b72841af26d93f35e169e19d86e5e8d667a","tid":944823,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"我剛讀梗HD，要揀科。<br />\n我揀左<span style=\"font-size: large;\">B</span>科，而A，C科（尤其<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></span>科）係我最唔想讀既科，我填選科表已經填左A係我<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最唔想讀，最冇興趣</span></span>嘅科。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">拿，我係果d拿臨搞掂啲學費就唔使煩嘅人。但因為我嗰幾日唔得閒所以冇去搞。</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">13號</span></span>佢出咗學費單，佢今日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">17號</span></span>vtc先打嚟同我講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「唔好意思，我哋搞錯咗呀，你所讀嘅科唔係B科，而係A科。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我吊你老母呀，好彩我冇早去交學費姐，如果唔係我咪俾錢去讀一個完全冇興趣嘅課程？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋點解你地可以咁冇交帶，話轉班就轉。一句話「搞錯咗」就算？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明明一開始就文件已經表示我係讀B科</span></span>，屌你老母突然間轉左去咁不負責任架咩？？？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪應該返去嘈佢，問可唔可以俾返B班個位我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以俾啲意見我？<br />\n關乎我人生㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26ef1d8cae00dc16a84a7f50d431c8a1486f36a","tid":944823,"uid":122570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"搵議員幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3790cd5766f60e7e649ba80026db260f4584ee5e","tid":944823,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46c34d64489e519a8b0caa4904d7fba414ce0da4","tid":944823,"uid":139322,"like":0,"disl